OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,FITV News' James Mates speaks to people
OL,7,Ffrom southern Lebanon who say that
OL,8,Fwhat Israel is repeating what it has
OL,9,Fdone in Gaza in their communities
OL,11,FAdditional reporting by ITV News
OL,12,FContent Editor Jessica Omari
OL,14,FWhat we saw in southern Lebanon did
OL,15,Fnot look like acts of war, carried out
OL,16,Fin the heat of battle.
OL,18,FThis was the deliberate, systematic
OL,19,Fdestruction of whole Lebanese villages
OL,20,Fin the name of fighting Hezbollah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
