OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,FWith each passing week, more and more
OL,7,Fof southern Lebanon is left looking
OL,8,Flike a desolate landscape.
OL,10,FA white wall marks the border: on one
OL,11,Fside we saw pristine and untouched
OL,12,FIsraeli homes; on the other, just
OL,13,Frubble.
OL,15,FWhat Israel has done in Gaza, it
OL,16,Fproudly says it is doing in Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
