OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,FIsrael's Defence Minister Israel Katz
OL,7,Fsummed up his plans in March by
OL,8,Fsaying: "All the houses in the
OL,9,Fvillages close to the border would be
OL,10,Fdemolished, according to the model of
OL,11,FBeit Hanoun and Rafah in Gaza strip."
OL,13,FWe travelled as far south as we could
OL,14,Fsafely go in Lebanon, to the Abbasiyah
OL,15,FIntersection in Tyre - anything
OL,16,Ftravelling further south is subject to
OL,17,Fattack.
OL,26,@pD@IOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
