CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781294762
OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,FThe world is not allowed to see
OL,7,Fanything the Israeli military is doing
OL,8,Ffurther south, exactly as happened in
OL,9,FGaza.
OL,11,FSo, the evidence we have is what we
OL,12,Fcan collect from phone footage and
OL,13,Feyewitness accounts.
OL,15,FIn the village of Mays al Jabal not a
OL,16,Fhouse remains standing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
