OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,FFatima Shkair's family home has been
OL,7,Freduced to nothing. She told us her
OL,8,Fpossessions, memories and even final
OL,9,Fresting places of her family members,
OL,10,Fare gone.
OL,12,F"Everything related to the good old
OL,13,Ftimes, was there, they also destroyed
OL,14,Fthe graves, now we are not able to
OL,15,Fdistinguish between the graves of my
OL,16,Fgrandma, my grandpa, my uncle, my
OL,17,Faunt," she said.
OL,19,F"Now we cannot distinguish the exact
OL,20,Fspot (where they are buried)."
OL,26,@tD@AOU|D@Fpm|D@\pn|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
