OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,FLubnan Balbaaki is a principal
OL,7,Fconductor of the Lebanese Philharmonic
OL,8,FOrchestra.
OL,10,FHis father, a leading artist, built
OL,11,Ftheir house in Aadaysit, and his
OL,12,Fchildren turned it into a museum of
OL,13,Ftheir father's work. None of this has
OL,14,Fsaved it from the demolition crews.
OL,16,FLubnan told us there was no fighting
OL,17,Fbetween Israel and Hezbollah in the
OL,18,Fhouse or in the area. But he said the
OL,19,Fhouse was still detonated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
