OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,F"There were bombs put there and then
OL,7,Fthe explosion happened," he told us,
OL,8,Fadding that it had destroyed much of
OL,9,Fhis father's life's work.
OL,11,F"There was a collection of at least
OL,12,F8,500 books in the house, as well as
OL,13,Fmy father's atelier".
OL,15,FThese heartbreaking stories go on and
OL,16,Fon, Sara Ismail showed us a selfie she
OL,17,Ftook in front of her home before the
OL,18,Fwar.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XO]sD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
