OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,FNow a refugee in Beirut, the next time
OL,7,Fshe saw it was on a video sent to her
OL,8,Fphone, surrounded by Israeli troops.
OL,10,FA satellite picture now reveals all
OL,11,Fthat is left of her village of Beit
OL,12,FLif. A moonscape. The homes of 7,000
OL,13,Fpeople bulldozed out of existence `
OL,14,F7,000 stories, each as painful as
OL,15,FSara's.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
