PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781294762
OL,3,C'Another Gaza': Israel is destroying
OL,4,Centire villages in southern Lebanon
OL,6,F"None of the houses are still
OL,7,Fstanding, even the hospital, the
OL,8,Fschool and the municipal buildings,"
OL,9,Fshe said, "as soon as this started, I
OL,10,Fasked myself, is this another Gaza
OL,11,Fhappening here in Lebanon?"
OL,13,FHow can people return to this? There
OL,14,Fare powerful voices in Israel urging
OL,15,Fthat 600,000 people never be allowed
OL,16,Fback to live here.
OL,18,FThat is the abiding dread of the three
OL,19,Fwho told us their story, three voices
OL,20,Fwho speak for so many.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@dO]qD@KOUsD@[O]
